value.text: 13 digits formatted in 5 groups separated by "-", where the 1st group must be "978" or "979". When the 1st group is "978", the 2nd group has 1 digit "0" to "5" or "7", or 3 digits starting by "6", or 2 digits starting by "8", or 2 to 5 digits starting by "9". The last 5th group is a single check digit.

13 chiffres formatés en 5 groupes séparés par "-", où le 1er groupe doit être "978" ou "979". Lorsque le 1er groupe est "978", le 2e est 1 chiffre "0" à "5" ou "7", ou 3 chiffres débutant par "6", ou 2 chiffres débutant par "8", ou 2 à 5 chiffres débutant par "9". Le dernier 5e groupe est un unique chiffre de contrôle.
13位數字，分為5組，中間用“-”分隔，其中第一組必須為“ 978”或“ 979”。 當第一組為“ 978”時，第二組具有“ 0”至“ 5”或“ 7”的一位數字，或以“ 6”開頭的3位數字，或以“ 8”開頭的2位數字，或2至5位數字 以“ 9”開頭。 最後的第5組是單個校驗位。

not convertible back to ISBN-10 for books published since 1 January 2007 (or any book using another prefix than "978-"); converting old books back to their original ISBN-10, published up to December 2006 (and found with an ISBN-13 in some digital catalogs), requires dropping the "978-" prefix AND recomputing the last check digit (or letter 'X') with the former algorithm.
